properties.Name: StoreIndicatorType
properties.Description:
A means of categorizing Store Indicators by functions performed, characteristics or similar common characteristics.

Ex:
- Online Ordering Available
- Pharmacy
- Pharmacy open to Midnight
- 24-hour Pharmacy
- 24-Hour Store
- Optician
- Public Bathroom
